"replies":15,"id":887451},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340","name":"qna","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340","title":"问与答","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","topics":191431,"footer":"","header":"一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。","title_alternative":"Questions and Answers","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340","stars":3585,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":12,"parent_node_name":"v2ex"},"member":{"id":244239,"username":"hzzz0823","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/hzzz0823","website":null,"twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":null,"tagline":null,"bio":null,"avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/9d02574487f96f1a9b0ea10d329f644b?s=24&d=retro","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/9d02574487f96f1a9b0ea10d329f644b?s=48&d=retro","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/9d02574487f96f1a9b0ea10d329f644b?s=73&d=retro","created":1500891216,"last_modified":1500891216},"last_reply_by":"fox0001","last_touched":1665986669,"title":"早教中心怎么选择","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/887473","created":1665977900,"deleted":0,"content":"孩子 11 个月，父母都比较内向，平时孩子妈妈全职带，小区里基本没什么机会和其他同龄小孩接触（只认识到一个）。所以想报个课，多见见其他孩子玩一玩。\r\n\r\n\r\n0. 有必要吗？（钱的方面属于有点影响生活，但也算是能承担… 我是觉得月开支中，吞金兽的额度早晚会涨到一个界限。 早晚躲不开这笔“月供”，提前承受点压力就承受吧。）\r\n\r\n1. 报课后，非上课时间是不是也能带孩子去公共区域玩？\r\n2. 这两个怎么选：距离近但是氛围不好；距离远但是氛围更满意的。（比如距离打分为 5 和 3 ，氛围打分为 2 和 4. 求和时候这个权重有没有什么经验）\r\n3. 坐标南京，有没有推荐，大概价格多少，100/课？","content_rendered":"<p>孩子 11 个月，父母都比较内向，平时孩子妈妈全职带，小区里基本没什么机会和其他同龄小孩接触（只认识到一个）。所以想报个课，多见见其他孩子玩一玩。</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>有必要吗？（钱的方面属于有点影响生活，但也算是能承担… 我是觉得月开支中，吞金兽的额度早晚会涨到一个界限。 早晚躲不开这笔“月供”，提前承受点压力就承受吧。）</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>报课后，非上课时间是不是也能带孩子去公共区域玩？</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>这两个怎么选：距离近但是氛围不好；距离远但是氛围更满意的。（比如距离打分为 5 和 3 ，氛围打分为 2 和 4. 求和时候这个权重有没有什么经验）</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>坐标南京，有没有推荐，大概价格多少，100/课？</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n","last_modified":1665977900,"replies":14,"id":887473},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e7b2/4b11/360_large.png?m=1641783557","name":"windows","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e7b2/4b11/360_normal.png?m=1641783557","title":"Windows","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/windows","topics":2941,"footer":"","header":"Windows, not walls.","title_alternative":"Windows","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e7b2/4b11/360_mini.png?m=1641783557","stars":957,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":360,"parent_node_name":"os"},"member":{"id":274063,"username":"shintendo","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/shintendo","website":null,"twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":null,"tagline":null,"bio":null,"avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/8627/ca70/274063_mini.png?m=1663236614","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/8627/ca70/274063_normal.png?m=1663236614","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/8627/ca70/274063_large.png?m=1663236614","created":1513070400,"last_modified":1663236614},"last_reply_by":"xuanbg","last_touched":1665972705,"title":"Win11 一个非常难受的细节","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/887417","created":1665970759,"deleted":0,"content":"如果你在最大化窗口的状态下关闭资源管理器，那么下次打开时仍然是最大化的。\r\n\r\n但是如果从外部程序唤起资源管理器（例如：chrome 下载文件后“打开所在文件夹”），此时跳出来的窗口是常规大小，停顿一下，然后自动进行一个最大化的动画。\r\n\r\n视觉上非常难受。","content_rendered":"<p>如果你在最大化窗口的状态下关闭资源管理器，那么下次打开时仍然是最大化的。</p>\n<p>但是如果从外部程序唤起资源管理器（例如：chrome 下载文件后“打开所在文件夹”），此时跳出来的窗口是常规大小，停顿一下，然后自动进行一个最大化的动画。</p>\n<p>视觉上非常难受。</p>\n","last_modified":1665970773,"replies":13,"id":887417},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c81e/728d/2_large.png?m=1497247332","name":"v2ex","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c81e/728d/2_normal.png?m=1497247332","title":"V2EX","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/v2ex","topics":3584,"footer":"","header":"这里讨论和发布关于 V2EX 站点的发展。","title_alternative":"V2EX","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c81e/728d/2_mini.png?m=1497247332","stars":1246,"aliases":[],"root":true,"id":2,"parent_node_name":"v2ex"},"member":{"id":434022,"username":"gromit1337